Frequently asked questionsLet’s set your mind at ease.Can’t find the answer you’re looking for? Reach out to our customer support team.Where can I read the API documentation?Our API documentation is available here.How do I get started with the API?You’ll first want to book a demo with a member of our team. After that, you can generate test API keys from your dashboard to integrate and test the API functionalities.What SDKs are available?Users can choose from three available SDKs: Java, Python, and Ruby. We have documentation for direct integration with our public endpoint if you have a different technology stack.Is the API setup to handle multiple different currencies?We support tracking the currencies used for Customer Currency, Filing Currency, and Functional Currency.Can the API handle shipping and handling charges?Shipping and handling charges should be treated as their own distinct products and line items. When it’s time to calculate taxes, you can pass the shipping costs as another line item to the tax/calculations endpoint.

